            . I live by Stepney church. On the 13th of March, about twelve o'clock, I sent my grandson, William Kent, with a bundle, containing these articles, to take about two hundred yards, to his mother's, to be washed - he returned and told me they were gone.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM KENT. I am eight years and a half old. My grandmother sent me with a bundle to my mother's for the things to be washed; the prisoner met me, and asked me to go down <placeName id="t18260406-262-crimeloc1418">Globe-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-262-crimeloc1418" type="placeName" value="Globe-lane"></interp>
