                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-262-off1416 t18260406-262-crimeloc1418"></join> to get two bundles of silk; and said, he would hold my bundle - I gave it to him - and when I came back he was gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260406-262-person1426">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MOGRIDGE
